{"type": "article", "id": 29580, "title": "自动换水的鱼缸", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:09:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160713214924Io6miWlq1JUwGRKE.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>养鱼最麻烦的莫过于换水和清洗鱼缸了，Craig Wenger 和 David Turover 这两位美国设计师曾在几年前推出了一款会自动换水的鱼缸，无需依靠其他工具就能在加水时自动排出缸里原有的污水。最近他们将当年的明星产品重新改良，推出了迭代版 GravityFlow 2。它仍然保留了利用水压自动换水这一便利又环保的功能：一旦缸内的水到达一定水位，底部的污水就会顺着管子排出，直到水压不足以推开管子底部的盖子为止。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/930441187/noclean-aquariums-eco-friendly-self-cleaning-glass\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 59 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607132149572DuoGfjLmnz8EQ6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713214957sk7RHQc4WheqzdOD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713214957MN5gmdBqTJKeUYHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713214957WMxzqJ04YtUGBpD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.507353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}